OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FTwo Church of England charities have
OL,7,Fbeen reprimanded by a watchdog over
OL,8,Fsafeguarding failures which led to the
OL,9,Fresignation of a bishop amid
OL,10,Fallegations of sexual assault and
OL,11,Fharassment.
OL,13,FThe Charity Commission said it is the
OL,14,Ffirst time it has issued an official
OL,15,Fwarning against any Church of England
OL,16,Fdiocese.
