OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FThe Liverpool Diocesan Board of
OL,7,FFinance and the Chelmsford Diocesan
OL,8,FBoard of Finance were said to have
OL,9,Ffailed to properly handle safeguarding
OL,10,Fallegations against John Perumbalath,
OL,11,Fwho was then the bishop of Liverpool
OL,12,Fand formerly bishop of Bradwell in the
OL,13,Fdiocese of Chelmsford.
OL,15,FBoth are registered charities which
OL,16,Faim to promote the work of the Church
OL,17,Fof England in their respective
OL,18,Fdioceses.
