OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FMr Perumbalath stepped down as bishop
OL,7,Fof Liverpool without any admission of
OL,8,Ffault or liability after Channel 4
OL,9,FNews reported that one woman had
OL,10,Faccused him of kissing her without
OL,11,Fconsent and groping her, and another
OL,12,Faccused him of sexual harassment.
OL,14,FIt came at a tumultuous time for the
OL,15,FChurch of England over various
OL,16,Fsafeguarding failures, which had just
OL,17,Fmonths earlier seen Justin Welby quit
OL,18,Fas archbishop of Canterbury over the
OL,19,Fhandling of a separate case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
