OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FThe commission said failings in
OL,7,Fhandling allegations against Mr
OL,8,FPerumbalath "amount to mismanagement
OL,9,Fin the administration of the two
OL,10,Fcharities".
OL,12,FThe regulator said that in both
OL,13,Finstances, "due to lack of appropriate
OL,14,Fprocedures and processes", trustees in
OL,15,Fthe two diocesan charities "who knew
OL,16,Fof the allegations failed to take
OL,17,Faction that would have allowed the
OL,18,Ftrustee boards to fully consider any
OL,19,Frisks and make a decision on the
OL,20,Fappropriate action to take".
