OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FThe commission said there were
OL,7,F"insufficient processes and procedures
OL,8,Fin place to ensure adequate oversight
OL,9,Fof safeguarding and protection of
OL,10,Fthose who come into contact with the
OL,11,Fcharity".
OL,13,FThe warning for the Chelmsford charity
OL,14,Ffound there had been a "failure
OL,15,Fongoing over a period of about two
OL,16,Fyears" to report a serious incident to
OL,17,Fthe commission relating to a complaint
OL,18,Fmade in January 2023 about allegations
OL,19,Fof sexual misconduct by Mr Perumbalath
OL,20,Fwhen he was bishop of Bradwell.
