OL,6,FTrustees of the Liverpool charity, it
OL,7,Ffound, "failed to consider or
OL,8,Finvestigate" a complaint against Mr
OL,9,FPerumbalath and failed to "act in the
OL,10,Fcharity's best interests and to take
OL,11,Freasonable steps to protect from harm
OL,12,Fpeople who come into contact with the
OL,13,Fcharity".
