OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FCommission Chief Executive David
OL,7,FHoldsworth said: "In the two diocesan
OL,8,Fcharities, lack of appropriate
OL,9,Fpolicies and procedures led to a
OL,10,Ffailure to ensure that serious
OL,11,Fallegations against a senior figure
OL,12,Fwere properly considered by the
OL,13,Frelevant trustee bodies.
OL,15,F"We will further engage with both
OL,16,Fcharities as they continue to take
OL,17,Fsteps to address our concerns."
