OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FBishop of Chelmsford Guli Francis-
OL,7,FDehqani and the Chelmsford diocesan
OL,8,Fsafeguarding officer, Amanda Knight,
OL,9,Fsaid in a joint statement they
OL,10,F"respectfully disagree" with some of
OL,11,Fthe commission's conclusions and were
OL,12,F"disappointed" by the decision to
OL,13,Fissue an official warning, which they
OL,14,Fbranded "disproportionate".
OL,16,FThey insisted the response to the
OL,17,F"complex case" had been "robust and
OL,18,Fsurvivor-led".
