OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,FIts chair of trustees said: "The
OL,7,FCharity Commission has issued a formal
OL,8,Fwarning to the trustees of the
OL,9,FLiverpool Diocesan Board of Finance.
OL,10,FThis follows an investigation by the
OL,11,Fcommission into the circumstances that
OL,12,Fled to the resignation of the former
OL,13,Fbishop of Liverpool, the Right
OL,14,FReverend John Perumbalath, in January
OL,15,F2025.
OL,26,@nD@]OU
