OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,F"Allegations were raised against the
OL,7,Fformer bishop of Liverpool in 2023.
OL,8,FThese allegations were denied;
OL,9,Fhowever, the commission has found that
OL,10,Ftrustees did not adequately discharge
OL,11,Ftheir safeguarding responsibilities in
OL,12,Frelation to the reporting of these
OL,13,Fallegations and that there were
OL,14,Ffailings in our processes and
OL,15,Fprocedures.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
