OL,3,CChurch of England charities 'failed'
OL,4,Con bishop safeguarding allegations
OL,6,F"We accept the commission's findings
OL,7,Fand apologise for the shortcomings
OL,8,Fidentified. We have already made
OL,9,Fchanges to strengthen reporting and
OL,10,Fgovernance processes, and we commit to
OL,11,Fongoing learning, accountability and
OL,12,Fcontinuous improvement.
OL,14,F"The Diocese of Liverpool is dedicated
OL,15,Fto ensuring that the Church is a safe
OL,16,Fand inclusive environment where
OL,17,Fconcerns can be raised in a culture of
OL,18,Faccountability, transparency and
OL,19,Fcompassion."
