OL,6,FThey added: "As a Church, our priority
OL,7,Fin all our safeguarding work remains
OL,8,Fto continue to improve our practice
OL,9,Fand respond well to victims and
OL,10,Fsurvivors.
OL,12,F"This includes the implementation of
OL,13,Ffurther safeguarding reforms,
OL,14,Fparticularly in governance, with
OL,15,Fdetailed proposals to be brought to
OL,16,Fnext month's General Synod to ensure
OL,17,Fsustainable and long-lasting best
OL,18,Fpractice."
