OL,6,FLast year, Mr Perumbalath stressed he
OL,7,Fhad consistently denied the
OL,8,Fallegations against him and said he
OL,9,Fhad complied with any investigation
OL,10,Ffrom the Church's safeguarding team.
OL,12,FIn a statement at the end of January
OL,13,F2025, he said: "Whilst I don't believe
